" buffer local mapping to switch to dfm or pas file
nmap <buffer> <nowait> <leader>sd :call delphi#SwitchPasOrDfm()<CR>
nmap <buffer> <nowait> <leader>sp :call delphi#SwitchPasOrDfm()<CR>

